-- J.C. Penney expects to raise up to $932 million from share offering
-- 
-- Fri Sep 27, 2013 7:35am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/09/27/us-jcpenney-offering-pricing-idUSBRE98Q0HT20130927

 

 (Reuters) - J.C. Penney Co Inc ( JCP.N ) will raise up to $932 million from a share offering of 96.6 million shares at $9.65 each. 
 The offering includes a 30-day option for underwriters to buy 12.6 million shares, the company said on Friday. The retailer's shares fell 6 percent to $9.79 in premarket trading. The public offering is expected to close on October 1, J.C. Penney said in a statement. (Reporting by  Siddharth Cavale  in Bangalore; Editing by Kirti Pandey)